## Build loop (repeat per app)

| Phase | Actions |
|-------|---------|
| **Build** | Capacitor shell, polish UI, icons/splash, AdMob test IDs documented |
| **Test** | `npm run mobile:preflight` → `npm run build` → `npm run mobile:sync` → device checklist |
| **Debug** | Fix JS/touch/offline/load; add 1–2 user-value features from `APP_DEV.md` |
| **GitHub** | Commit per app → `git push origin main` — **STOP and report if push fails** |
| **TestFlight** | Bump version, update `mobile/store-metadata/`, mark **READY** in `APP_DEV.md` |
| **Next** | Start next app immediately |

